*** BUILDING ON WINDOWS ***

You will need WinAVR (I used WinAVR-20090313) from here:

  http://winavr.sourceforge.net

...and Atmel's FLIP tool from here:

  http://www.atmel.com/dyn/products/tools_card.asp?tool_id=3886

...for loading code to the AVR over USB.

Then just do this:

  make
  make flash


*** BUILDING ON LINUX ***

You will need gcc-avr, avr-libc and dfu-programmer, e.g

  sudo apt-get install gcc-avr
  sudo apt-get install avr-libc
  sudo apt-get install dfu-programmer

Then just do this:

  make
  sudo make dfu

